Helpful notes:
    *standardized table header titles and tuple ordering*
    _LEAGUE -> league_name VARCHAR, country VARCHAR, sponsor VARCHAR, current_champ VARCHAR, num_teams INTEGER
    _TEAM   -> team_name VARCHAR, league VARCHAR, city VARCHAR, sponsor VARCHAR, year_founded INTEGER, manager VARCHAR, kit VARCHAR, points INTEGER, goals INTEGER, assists INTEGER, cards INTEGER
    _PLAYER -> player_name VARCHAR, jersey_num INTEGER, team VARCHAR, position VARCHAR, goals INTEGER, assists INTEGER, cards INTEGER, starter VARCHAR

